    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CategoriesId], [p].[CreatedAtUtc], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[SKU], [p].[StockAmount], [p].[UnitPrice], [p].[UnitType], [p].[UpdatedAtUtc], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CategoriesId], [p].[CreatedAtUtc], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[SKU], [p].[StockAmount], [p].[UnitPrice], [p].[UnitType], [p].[UpdatedAtUtc], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[SKU] LIKE @__ToLower_0_contains ESCAPE N'\'
    ORDER BY [p].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [c].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
